{"analytics_identifier":"OT1412","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-centre-for-climate-health-security","content_id":"b4330006-d9c0-4dda-9bb1-88a2bb55aafe","description":"The Centre for Climate and Health Security provides scientific advice to partners at all levels ensuring climate change and extreme weather impacts on public health are included in system design. CCHS is part of the UK Health Security Agency .","details":{"acronym":"CCHS","alternative_format_contact_email":"publications@UKHSA.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Centre for Climate and Health Security provides scientific advice to partners at all levels ensuring climate change and extreme weather impacts on public health are included in system design.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Centre for Climate and Health Security\">CCHS</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/uk-health-security-agency\">UK Health Security Agency</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-of-health","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Centre for Climate and Health Security"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Research","href":"/government/publications/climate-change-and-mental-health-report","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69148d6dbc34c86ce4e6e6a1/s712_cchs_mh_landing.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69148d6d493305b49ce6e6a6/s465_cchs_mh_landing.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69148d6ddb01ecfcf96fc851/cchs_mh_landing.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-13T09:30:13.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The climate change and mental health thematic assessment report synthesises the evidence base relating to climate change and mental health.</p>\n</div>","title":"Climate change and mental health report"},{"document_type":"Document collection","href":"/government/collections/climate-related-hazards","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67c977ded0fba2f1334cf2fe/s712_CCHS_climate_hazards.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67c977df696e4984ea4cf2e5/s465_CCHS_climate_hazards.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67c977de75d7505462fc6620/CCHS_climate_hazards.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-09-24T09:51:58.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Discover more about heat, cold weather, flooding and other weather-related hazards such as droughts, storms and wildfires. These pages are under development and some topics are not yet available.</p>\n</div>","title":"Climate-related hazards"},{"document_type":"Document collection","href":"/government/collections/health-impacts","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67c97b42ae2aa47d2f5ae37c/s712_cchs_health_impacts.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67c97b428247839c255ae388/s465_cchs_health_impacts.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/67c97b422ecc810ad1fc662d/cchs_health_impacts.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-12T10:13:44.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Discover more about vector borne disease, antimicrobial resistant infections, mental health, co-morbidities and other health impacts such as food-borne and fungal illness. These pages are under development and some topics are not yet available.</p>\n</div>","title":"Climate health impacts"},{"document_type":"Document collection","href":"/government/collections/environmental-exposures","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6894d2c1a6eb81a3f9b2e281/s712_environmental_hazards.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6894d2c1e7be62b4f064316b/s465_environmental_hazards.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6894d2c1a6eb81a3f9b2e280/environmental_hazards.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-08-07T00:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Discover more about airborne allergens, air quality, water quality and other environmental exposures such as chemicals and radiation. These pages are under development and some topics are not yet available.</p>\n</div>","title":"Environmental exposures"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/cchs-page-structure","title":"CCHS page structure"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"sub_organisation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2024-04-08T13:34:46+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1412","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/the-centre-for-climate-health-security","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/the-centre-for-climate-health-security","base_path":"/government/organisations/the-centre-for-climate-health-security","content_id":"b4330006-d9c0-4dda-9bb1-88a2bb55aafe","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-12-23T09:11:52Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Centre for Climate and Health Security","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-centre-for-climate-health-security","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA1328","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/uk-health-security-agency","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/uk-health-security-agency","base_path":"/government/organisations/uk-health-security-agency","content_id":"80091cd8-7a8f-41ef-8faf-8af91fce4fdb","details":{"acronym":"UKHSA","brand"